properties.headline: FLOODING - COONAMBLE SHIRE COUNCIL Local roads
properties.otherAdvice:
Coonamble Shire Council wishes to advise the travelling public that ALL UNSEALED ROADS within the Shire are CLOSED TO ALL TRAFFIC.

Quambone Rd, between Coonamble and Quambone, is also closed due to Euronne Gully flooding.

Please refer to the council website or call (02) 6827 1900 for further information.
